OL,5, A former pupil of Fettes College has   
OL,6, secured a settlement of #400,000 from  
OL,7, the school after alleging he was abused
OL,8, by a teacher.                          
OL,10,FIn evidence to the Scottish Child Abuse
OL,11,FInquiry, the man known as Frank claimed
OL,12,Fhe was beaten and sexually abused at   
OL,13,Fthe Edinburgh school.                  
OL,15,FFettes has previously offered a "full  
OL,16,Fand unreserved apology" to those who   
OL,17,Fsuffered abuse while at the school.    
OL,19,FFollowing the payment, the man said:   
OL,20,F"It has never been about the money".   
